                " Statistical errors are presented."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The reaction d(g-pol,np) has been studied using the",
                " tagged and polarized LADON gamma-ray beam at an",
                " energy 30 - 50 MeV to investigate the existence of",
                " narrow dibaryonic resonances recently suggested from",
                " the experimental measurements in different",
                " laboratories. The beam was obtained by Compton",
                " back-scattering of laser light on the electrons of",
                " storage ring ADONE. Photo-neutron yields were",
                " measured at five neutron angles (theta-n) -c.m. = 22,",
                " 55.5, 90, 125 and 157 degree in the center of mass",
                " system."
              ]
            }
          ],
